            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/legacy/8.html">16th ShipIt Day</a> - August 2017
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/legacy/7.html">15th ShipIt Day</a> - April 2017
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/legacy/6.html">14th ShipIt Day</a> - March 2016
